{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01793Xonjqr2qL7yiTNVBbFz","type":"tool_result","content":"  5200→| verify | $383.41 | 54.2% |\n  5201→| orchestrator | $146.31 | 20.7% |\n  5202→| retro | $74.35 | 10.5% |\n  5203→| code-review | $36.74 | 5.2% |\n  5204→| create-story | $36.58 | 5.2% |\n  5205→| dev-story | $30.07 | 4.3% |\n  5206→\n  5207→### Waste attribution\n  5208→\n  5209→- **\"unknown\" story: $160.87 (22.7%)** — This bucket contains orchestrator overhead, state corruption fixes, and no-op session costs. A significant portion of this $160.87 is waste from sessions 17-47.\n  5210→- **\"1-1-foo\" phantom story: $23.59 (3.3%)** — Entirely wasted on a phantom story that never existed. Created by Ralph's stale state, repeatedly fixed and re-created.\n  5211→- **Estimated waste from no-op sessions: ~$151.40** (delta between session 30 and 47 cost reports).\n  5212→\n  5213→## 4. What Went Well\n  5214→\n  5215→- Each individual fix was efficient (~11 tool calls, ~3 minutes). The pattern is well-understood.\n  5216→- Subagents reported zero redundant operations within sessions — they diagnosed and fixed quickly.\n  5217→- Sprint completed successfully: 74/74 stories, 17/17 epics, all verified with proof documents.\n  5218→\n  5219→## 5. What Went Wrong\n  5220→\n  5221→1. **Ralph was not killed after sprint completion.** This has been a P0 action item since session 17. It was never executed. 31 sessions of waste followed.\n  5222→2. **No circuit breaker exists.** Ralph has no mechanism to detect \"I am doing the same thing every iteration\" and halt.\n  5223→3. **No sprint-complete detection.** Ralph has no check for `doneCount === totalCount` to auto-terminate.\n  5224→4. **Monotonic status guard never implemented.** A guard that rejects `done` -> `review` transitions when proof docs exist would have prevented all 31 corruption instances.\n  5225→5. **Retros accumulated cost on no-op sessions.** The retro phase alone cost $74.35 (10.5% of total). A significant portion of that is from retros on sessions that did nothing.\n  5226→\n  5227→## 6. Lessons Learned\n  5228→\n  5229→1. **Autonomous agents need kill switches.** When a sprint is complete, Ralph must terminate. There is no \"just in case\" reason to keep iterating.\n  5230→2. **State writes must be idempotent and monotonic.** A story that has been verified and marked `done` with proof documents must never be reverted to an earlier status by any process.\n  5231→3. **The cost of not acting on P0 items is concrete and measurable.** \"Kill Ralph\" was flagged as P0 in session 17. Ignoring it cost $151.40.\n  5232→4. **Circuit breakers are not optional for autonomous loops.** If the last N iterations performed identical operations, the system must halt and escalate.\n  5233→5. **Retros on no-op sessions should be 1-line entries, not full documents.** This retro itself is contributing to the waste.\n  5234→\n  5235→## 7. Action Items\n  5236→\n  5237→| Priority | Action | Owner | Status |\n  5238→|----------|--------|-------|--------|\n  5239→| **P0** | **Kill Ralph NOW.** `kill $(cat ralph/.pid)` or equivalent. Sprint is done. There is nothing left to do. | User | OVERDUE x31 — first flagged session 17 |\n  5240→| **P0** | **Add sprint-complete auto-termination to Ralph.** `if (doneCount === totalCount) process.exit(0)`. | Next sprint planning | NOT STARTED |\n  5241→| **P0** | **Add monotonic status guard.** Reject any transition from `done` to an earlier status when a proof document exists in `verification/`. | Next sprint planning | NOT STARTED |\n  5242→| **P1** | **Add circuit breaker.** If last N sessions performed identical state corrections, halt and alert the user. | Next sprint planning | NOT STARTED |\n  5243→| **P1** | **Re-read state from disk before every write.** Ralph must not rely on stale in-memory state. | Next sprint planning | NOT STARTED |\n  5244→| **P1** | **Skip retros on no-op sessions.** If `storiesAttempted === 0 && storiesCompleted === 0`, emit a 1-line entry, not a full retro. | Process improvement | NOT STARTED |\n  5245→| **P2** | **Audit \"unknown\" cost bucket.** $160.87 attributed to no story. Break this down by session to quantify waste precisely. | Post-mortem | NOT STARTED |\n  5246→\n  5247→---\n  5248→\n  5249→**Session 47 is the 17th consecutive no-op session and the 31st state corruption fix. $151.40 wasted since sprint completion. The sprint has been done for 31+ sessions. KILL RALPH.**"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Q3L9zZDjMfxttP7jXVjVsm","session_id":"d3007834-189d-4ff7-85a3-989699e3cb8f","uuid":"160773ec-fa5e-4600-ae02-257fa4317bda","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:37:20.214Z"}
